# Docs Sync Rule

- When implementation status changes, update related docs in the same task.
- Keep `frontend/README.md` roadmap and checklist aligned with repository reality.
- Avoid aspirational wording that implies features are complete when they are not.
- Add short notes for major scope decisions, deferrals, and launch-impacting trade-offs.
- Ensure onboarding, auth, and feature flow docs match current app behavior.
- Treat outdated documentation as technical debt that must be closed quickly.
